        "title": "[codex] docs: clarify Skill Workshop tool visibility",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n\r\n- Sync the policy plugin's tool-group conformance map and add focused coverage so group:agents and group:openclaw match the documented goal-tool and skill_workshop expansion.\r\n- Update the tools profile table so `coding` and `messaging` reflect the current core tool catalog, including `skill_workshop` and `bundle-mcp`.\n- Add Skill Workshop tool-visibility guidance for agents where stricter profile, provider/agent policy, or `tools.deny` hides the manual `skill_workshop` tool.\n- Sync the sandbox/tool-policy shorthand table so `group:agents` matches the same goal-tool and `skill_workshop` expansion.\n\nRefs #87570.\n\n## Verification\n\n\r\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/policy/src/tool-policy-conformance.test.ts` (blocked locally before assertions: incomplete Windows dependency install is missing `@rolldown/binding-win32-x64-msvc` after two `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` attempts)\n- `git diff --check HEAD~1 HEAD`\n- PowerShell exact policy group check for `group:agents` and `group:openclaw`\r\n- `pnpm docs:list`\n- `npx oxfmt --check docs/gateway/config-tools.md docs/tools/skill-workshop.md docs/gateway/sandbox-vs-tool-policy-vs-elevated.md`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `rg -n \"group:agents\" docs/gateway/config-tools.md docs/gateway/sandbox-vs-tool-policy-vs-elevated.md`\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: The public docs now describe the current `skill_workshop` and goal-tool visibility behavior consistently across the tool profile docs and the sandbox/tool-policy shorthand docs.\n\nReal environment tested: Local OpenClaw docs checkout with the source docs and docs-list script.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: Ran `rg -n \"group:agents\" docs/gateway/config-tools.md docs/gateway/sandbox-vs-tool-policy-vs-elevated.md` after the docs edits.\n\nEvidence after fix: Terminal output from the final docs grep:\n\n```text\ndocs/gateway/sandbox-vs-tool-policy-vs-elevated.md:101:- `group:agents`: `agents_list`, `get_goal`, `create_goal`, `update_goal`, `update_plan`, `skill_workshop`\ndocs/gateway/config-tools.md:43:| `group:agents`     | `agents_list`, `get_goal`, `create_goal`, `update_goal`, `update_plan`, `skill_workshop`                                |\n```\n\nObserved result after fix: Both gateway docs now list the same `group:agents` expansion, including `get_goal`, `create_goal`, `update_goal`, `update_plan`, and `skill_workshop`.\n\nWhat was not tested: I did not run a live Gateway or publish the Mintlify site locally. The local focused Vitest command was attempted but could not reach assertions because the Windows checkout dependency install is incomplete (`@rolldown/binding-win32-x64-msvc` missing after two `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile` attempts).\n",
